com.events.database

Class DbConst

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.events.database.DbConst

  • public class DbConst
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class DbConst holds all the Database constants like database name, table names and field names and It also includes the strings for creating tables in Sqlite db.
